section.def:
College
                (學院) means the College of St. John the
            Evangelist;

constitution
                (憲章) means the constitution set out in the
                Schedule and any subsequent amendments thereto;

council
                (院務委員會) means the council of the College
            established in accordance with the constitution;

rules
                (規則) means rules made by the council under
                section 6;
